<span id="freeTextContainer16424812728456106140">A gem of a memoir. Richer than Spielberg&apos;s film (though he did an excellent job with the material). Mesmerizing from start to finish.</span>
  <span id="freeText16424812728456106140" style="display:none">A gem of a memoir. Richer than Spielberg's film (though he did an excellent job with the material). Mesmerizing from start to finish.</span>
