        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1556867999" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16213121071767027249">I loved this book. Ballard is a superb writer, and I felt as though I was living through the nightmare of Shanghai at the time. It is not a book for the faint-hearted as it is explicit and gory. But well worth the read to gain an insight into what the Chino-Japanese war was all about, phasing into WWII.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


